rows.label: tlk41100171_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, you guys look like you're
great at catching bugs!
I'm right, aren't I?!

rows.label: tlk41100171_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Listen, I'm making a specimen
collection!

rows.label: tlk41100171_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm so close to finishing, but there's
this one insect I can't find anywhere!

rows.label: tlk41100171_04_msg0004
rows.name:
I've searched high and low for it too...
Maybe it's just the wrong kind of
environment for it...

rows.label: tlk41100171_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Argh! If I knew someone who was
into bug-catching, I'd've totally
caught it by now!

rows.label: tlk41100171_04_msg0006
rows.name: Wha-?! You're really gonna help me?!

rows.label: tlk41100171_04_msg0007
rows.name: Oh, wow! Awesome! Thanks so much!
